title: Picnic Time's 101 Piece Tool Kit 700
transcripts: The 101 piece tool kit by Picnic Time is a top quality tool set and in an attractive and durable aluminum case. Made of steel and molded plastic, this set has any tool you might need for house hold repairs, automotive tuneups or basic building needs. This comprehensive array of commonly used tools has a unique interior molded tray that lifts out of the case to reveal the 39 piece socket wrench set. This set also includes, one adjustable wrench, one claw hammer, one pair of long nose pliers with cutters, one pair of blunt nose plies with cutters, a measuring tape, one utility knife with break off blades, one ten piece Allan wrench set, one hand driver with two sets of insert bits, one seven piece combination wrench set, one six piece combination screw driver set, four Phillips screwdrivers, five flat screw drivers, one pair of six position flat tongue-and groove pliers, and two medium sized empty storage containers with adjustable dividers. Amadeo project 101 piece tool kit has you covered.
